==個人生活==
拜爾斯生於美國[[哥伦布_(俄亥俄州)|俄亥俄州哥伦布市]]，她的母親香農（Shanon Biles）因酗酒和藥物問題，被美國社會局判定無法撫養小孩<ref name="World Champion Gymnast Focuses on Talent, Not Racism">{{cite web|title=Simone Biles looks past the international taunts to concentrate on training for the 2016 Olympics.|url=http://www.theroot.com/articles/culture/2013/11/gymnast_simone_biles_a_world_champion_s_life.html|publisher=HILLARY CROSLEY|accessdate=2013-11-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109064526/http://www.theroot.com/articles/culture/2013/11/gymnast_simone_biles_a_world_champion_s_life.html|archivedate=2013-11-09}}</ref>，拜爾斯與妹妹六歲前是在多個寄養家庭流浪，祖父羅納得·拜爾斯（Ronald Biles）得知後，與配偶納莉·拜爾斯（Nellie Biles）決定領養她與妹妹艾迪亞·拜爾斯（Adria Biles）並擔起撫育的重任。被爺爺領養的拜爾斯，青年之後，感受到撫育的恩慈，就改稱呼他們為爸媽而非祖父母。羅納得·拜爾斯與納莉·拜爾斯從原先的工作退休之後，2014年為拜爾斯在德州成立了體操訓練中心World Champions Centre，讓拜爾斯日常練習，不須舟車勞頓，更聘用拜爾斯的教練作為總教練<ref>{{cite web|title=Where Is Simone Biles' Gym? The Texas Center Was Built By Her Parents|url=https://www.romper.com/p/where-is-simone-biles-gym-the-texas-center-was-built-by-her-parents-16451|website=romper.com|publisher=romper.com|accessdate=2016-08-19|date=2016-08-16|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126053825/https://www.romper.com/p/where-is-simone-biles-gym-the-texas-center-was-built-by-her-parents-16451|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年夏天拜爾斯取得高中同等學歷，她是[[在家自學|在家自學]]系統的學生。<ref name="Simone Biles official site bio">{{cite web|title=Biography|url=http://www.gym-style.com/simonebiles/about.htm|publisher=Simone Biles Official Website|accessdate=2013-02-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130306071629/http://www.gym-style.com/simonebiles/about.htm|archivedate=2013-03-06}}</ref>

2014年8月4日，西蒙·拜爾斯在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上宣佈她決定在[[加州大学洛杉矶分校|加州大学洛杉矶分校]]唸大學，但會延遲到[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會]]之後才入學。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://olympictalk.nbcsports.com/2014/08/04/simone-biles-chooses-ucla-gymnastics-olympics/|title=Simone Biles chooses UCLA|publisher=[[NBC_Sports|NBC Sports]]|accessdate=2015-10-30|first1=Zaccardi|last1=Nick|date=2014-08-04|archive-date=2015-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150830085516/http://olympictalk.nbcsports.com/2014/08/04/simone-biles-chooses-ucla-gymnastics-olympics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年7月29日，拜爾斯宣佈她會轉為職業體操選手（可接受[[贊助商|贊助商]]投資），放棄她的[[國家大學體育協會|國家大學體育協會]]選手資格。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://olympictalk.nbcsports.com/2015/07/29/simone-biles-turns-professional-gymnastics-olympics-octagon/|title=Simone Biles turns pro|publisher=[[NBC_Sports|NBC Sports]]|accessdate=2015-10-30|first1=Zaccardi|last1=Nick|date=2015-07-29|archive-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724160059/https://olympics.nbcsports.com/2015/07/29/simone-biles-turns-professional-gymnastics-olympics-octagon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>拜爾斯的體育經紀商為Octagon公司，2015年她宣佈與[[Nike|Nike]]簽約接受贊助<ref>{{cite web|last1=Maine|first1=D'Arcy|title=Simone Biles Signs With Nike, Immediately Gets Invited By Shawn Johnson To 'Swoosh Party'|url=http://espn.go.com/espnw/athletes-life/the-buzz/article/14104535/simone-biles-signs-nike-immediately-gets-invited-shawn-johnson-swoosh-party|website=ESPN Women|accessdate=2015-12-12|date=2015-11-11|archive-date=2016-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160713042007/http://espn.go.com/espnw/athletes-life/the-buzz/article/14104535/simone-biles-signs-nike-immediately-gets-invited-shawn-johnson-swoosh-party|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Olympic Marketing Notes: U.S. Gymnast Simone Biles Signs Deal With Nike|url=https://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/Daily/Issues/2015/11/12/Marketing-and-Sponsorship/Oly-Marketing-Notes.aspx|website=SportsBusiness Daily|publisher=American City Business Journals.|accessdate=2015-12-12|date=2015-11-12|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122095228/https://www.sportsbusinessdaily.com/Daily/Issues/2015/11/12/Marketing-and-Sponsorship/Oly-Marketing-Notes.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外她同時也為競技體操[[服裝|服裝]]品牌[[GK_Elite_Sportswear|GK Elite Sportswear]]代言<ref>{{cite web|title=GK Signs Simone Biles as Newest Endorsed Athlete|url=http://blog.gkelite.com/2015/11/gk-signs-simone-biles-as-newest-endorsed-athlete/|website=GK|publisher=GK Elite Sportswear|accessdate=2015-12-12|date=2015-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151201063920/http://blog.gkelite.com/2015/11/gk-signs-simone-biles-as-newest-endorsed-athlete/|archive-date=2015-12-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

西蒙·拜爾斯在2018年1月18日在推特上留言，表示前[[美國體操協會|美國體操協會]]的隊醫[[拉里·纳萨尔|拉里·纳萨尔]]曾對她抗性侵（[[美国体操队性侵丑闻|美国体操队性侵丑闻]]）<ref>{{Cite web|date=2018-01-15|title=Simone Biles: I was sexually abused by USA Gymnastics doctor Larry Nassar|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/jan/15/simone-biles-larry-nassar-sexual-abuse-allegations-usa-gymnastics|access-date=2021-07-28|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211227080033/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/jan/15/simone-biles-larry-nassar-sexual-abuse-allegations-usa-gymnastics|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她也指名[[美國體操協會|美國體操協會]]讓性侵一事發生，而且之後設法掩蓋此事<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/01/15/us/simone-biles-larry-nassar/index.html|title=Simone Biles says Larry Nassar abused her|last=Grinberg|first=Emanuella|date=2018-01-16|work=[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]|access-date=2018-10-10|archive-date=2018-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210110943/https://www.cnn.com/2018/01/15/us/simone-biles-larry-nassar/index.html|url-status=live}}</ref>。她因為「對於要再面對拉里·纳萨尔，在情緒上還沒準備好」，因此沒有參加2018年1月16日至24日的聽證會<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/01/31/us/simone-biles-gymnast-nassar/index.html|title=Simone Biles: I wasn't emotionally ready to face Larry Nassar again|last=Levenson|first=Eric|date=2018-02-01|work=[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]|access-date=December 10, 2018|archive-date=2018-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210110903/https://www.cnn.com/2018/01/31/us/simone-biles-gymnast-nassar/index.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/24/sports/larry-nassar-sentencing.html|title=Larry Nassar Sentencing: 'I Just Signed Your Death Warrant'|last1=Cacciola|first1=Scott|date=2018-01-24|work=The New York Times|access-date=2018-10-10|last2=Mather|first2=Victor|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302201826/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/24/sports/larry-nassar-sentencing.html|url-status=live}}</ref>。2018年5月時宣佈西蒙·拜爾斯和其他被性侵的體操選手獲頒{{le|亞瑟·阿什勇氣獎|Arthur Ashe Courage Award}}。在2018年美國體操錦標賽中，西蒙設設計了一件青色緊身衣，並且穿著進行比賽，這是為了紀念被納薩爾性侵的選手，作為團結的聲明<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/olympics/gymnastics/story/_/id/24420472|title=Biles pays tribute to survivors in nationals sweep|date=2018-08-20|website=ESPN.com|language=en|access-date=2018-12-10|archive-date=2018-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210111240/http://www.espn.com/olympics/gymnastics/story/_/id/24420472|url-status=live}}</ref>。

